{
  "stem": "7455.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Probably beyond our neighborhood at those [INAUDIBLE] some people lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we heard them crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in Yiddish, Shema Israel, crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were leading them to the trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But when a siren-- then there's a siren, a loud siren, announcing that they met their quota.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now we can come out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we waited again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The next day I go back to work, and we waited for the inevitable to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There's no hope.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was at Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Schubert's-- ?] and she had many acquaintances with farmers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They had wholesale businesses, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "One time I was finished cleaning Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] room.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I'm coming-- coming into the kitchen, and I see some gentiles, some men, sitting there talking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I withdrew myself, because it's private.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "She said, no, come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Come in.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They were sitting discussing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "She was purchasing from them false Christian documents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Volks ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "German, ?] which means Germans-- Poles of German descent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Let's say the father was German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So they-- being that they are part German, they have in-- office positions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And when the Christians announced a new registration of the Christian population, new documents will be issued.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Therefore, separate them completely from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he was in that office where people had to-- people bring-- had [INAUDIBLE] ID photograph, and they had forms, give them your information.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And when they stamped that document, half of it was on the photograph, and half on the document.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "This way, you couldn't take a false-- a document and paste your picture on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There is no stamp on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "This way, it's bona fide that this is the real document.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were making money.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
